
# Embedded Routers
  + Can be defined using Play provided DSL
    - Called as 'String Interpolating Routing DSL'
  + Is useful for,
     - Embedding light weight play server ???:More
     - Providing custom/advanced routing capabilities to regular Play application
     - Mocking rest services for testing
     
# Reference
  + https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.6.x/ScalaRouting#Custom-routing     
  